util

Class AbstractToStringHelper

  • java.lang.Object
    • util.AbstractToStringHelper
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    ReflectiveToStringHelper, ToStringHelper

    public abstract class AbstractToStringHelper
extends Object
    A mutable String representation of an arbitrary object.

    This class imposes a single abstract method: toString(). The general contract of this method is to return the data represented by the object using an arbitrary formatting sequence.

    Author:
    Oliver Abdulrahim
